section.section:
"Bottle club" means a club, room, or premises:
That serves, sells, gives, or dispenses alcoholic beverages to its members or guests;
That keeps for its members or guests any alcoholic beverages;
That allows to be consumed by its members or guests on its premises any alcoholic beverages that have been reserved or purchased by the members or guests;
At which patrons are served, given, or allowed to consume alcoholic beverages after legal closing hours from the supplies that the patrons have previously purchased or reserved; or
That sells, dispenses, or serves to, keeps for, or allows to be consumed any setups or other component parts of mixed alcoholic drinks by its members or guests.
